      <title>美国推迟对越南市场经济地位作出决定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/us-delays-decision-on-vietnam-s-market-economy-status-by-a-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登政府宣布是否将越南列为市场经济的决定的时间已延长一周，将于 8 月 2 日之前公布，此举可能促进越南的出口。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/us-delays-decision-on-vietnam-s-market-economy-status-by-a-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 01:14:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
